A version of this story first appeared in CNN Business’ Before the Bell newsletter. Jeff Bezos got his phone hacked, perhaps by Saudi Arabia. But that might be the least of his problems.Amazon (AMZN) is facing a host of calls from both Republicans and Democrats for stricter regulation of the company and perhaps an antitrust investigation.The company is embroiled in a legal battle against the United States after the Trump administration passed over Amazon Web Services for a $10 billion cloud computing contract called JEDI.